e was 9.\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4351, \"end\": 4356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Moore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1401173857915894e-15, \"text\": \"Moore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Moore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Moore\"}, {\"begin\": 4362, \"end\": 4370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8777458687500564e-15, \"text\": \"Hawaiian\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}, {\"begin\": 4425, \"end\": 4433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\", \"score\": 0.9992203555896915, \"rank\": 0.0007789552874557228, \"text\": \"Caroline\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Kennedy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"posters\", \"from\": 4313, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"her first world title\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4400}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When her grandfather offered to buy her a horse, she declined, saying she just wanted to surf now.\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her grandfather\", \"from\": 4446, \"to\": 4461}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soon Caroline didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t just surf with her brothers; she tried to beat them.\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just surf\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4573}, {\"ngram\": \"her brothers\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some sessions ended in tears, but she always went back.\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4672, \"entities\": [], \"no