 off.\", \"from\": 13568, \"to\": 13797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13574, \"end\": 13584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.306073823220219e-28, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 13599, \"to\": 13603}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 13621, \"to\": 13630}, {\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 13652, \"to\": 13661}, {\"ngram\": \"always people\", \"from\": 13662, \"to\": 13675}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 13740, \"to\": 13749}, {\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 13783, \"to\": 13792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just something about being home in Florida that feels so grounded.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d And she went surfing with her family, right back where she caught her first waves.\", \"from\": 13798, \"to\": 13965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13847, \"end\": 13854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1715280471131281e-24, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 13798, \"to\": 13811}, {\"ngram\": \"just something\", \"from\": 13812, \"to\": 13826}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 13908, \"to\": 13918}, {\"ngram\": \"her first waves\", \"from\": 13948, \"to\": 13963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was so nice going surfing just, behind the house, with nobody else around,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\", \"from\": 13966, \"to\": 14059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 13966, \"to\": 13971}, {\"ngram\": \"so nice going surfi